#EV Quality Checklist ✅  
This repository contains a structured Quality Assurance (QA) checklist for Electric Vehicle (EV) manufacturing and assembly.  
The objective is to ensure **product reliability, safety, and compliance with EV industry standards**. 

## 🔹 Sections  

### 1. Battery Pack QA  
- Cell balancing verification  
- Thermal management system check  
- Battery casing and insulation test  
- Safety compliance (IEC/ISO standards)  

### 2. Electric Powertrain QA  
- Motor efficiency and performance check  
- Noise, vibration, and harshness (NVH) inspection  
- Controller and inverter functionality test  

### 3. Charging System QA  
- Fast/slow charging compatibility test  
- Charging connector safety inspection  
- Overload and auto cut-off verification  

### 4. Vehicle Assembly QA  
- Chassis and frame welding inspection  
- Wiring harness & connectors check  
- Brake, suspension & steering testing  

---

